				"img": "icons/magic/lightning/bolt-beam-strike-blue.webp",
				"description": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-412fd6ea-7fff-06e7-3a9d-91414e2560fb\"><strong>Shocking:</strong> On hit, target loses reaction for 1 round. Gains +1d4 expertise die to hit against targets wearing metal armor or made of metal (or imposes a -1d4 penalty to saves for such targets)</span></p>",
				"target": {
